summary: I am passionate about the role of education in transforming individuals, communities, and societies. I am an experienced Learning Specialist with demonstrated experience in both public and independent education sectors in the US and internationally. My strengths include education policy, advocacy work, building inclusive school culture, and organizational capacity building around supporting marginalized populations.
